column5: Hey, has anyone seen this yet?  This is just out of control!  Save the Sea Kittens  This is a notice to all you Parents, Teachers, Coaches etc. who fish and love the outdoors to teach your kids about fishing and the outdoors before they are  brain washed into being an ANTI!!!!!!!
